* Add Pick typings for setState/setProps, mirrors #13155

* Solve conflict: Old definitions was not allowing a GeometryCollection to be a GeometryObject, but the specification does! *[reference](http://geojson.org/geojson-spec.html#geometry-objects)*

* Add version to Header according to the specification revision: *[reference](http://geojson.org/geojson-spec.html)*
